.TH "TINYMEDIA" "1" "April 2026" ""
.SH "NAME"
\fBTinyMedia\fR \- Unobrtusive Music Player
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
\fBTinyMedia\fR is a widget to play music as unobtrusively as possible\. There are three buttons \- Play, Pause, and Next\. That's it\.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Tinymedia controls \fIMOC \- music on console\fR (https://moc\.daper\.net) from the system tray\. Click on the icon to get the control widget\. Right\-click on it to load an audio file or playlist\.
.SH "SUPPORTED FORMATS"
\fBMusic:\fR Most common formats\. \fI\.mp3\fR, \fI\.aac\fR, \fI\.aiff\fR, \fI\.midi\fR, \fI\.ogg\fR, \fI\.wav\fR etc\. \fBPlaylists:\fR \fI\.m3u\fR playlists\.
.SH "HOMEPAGE"
https://github\.com/primatelab/TinyMedia
